<script type="text/javascript">
    $(document).ready(function () {        
        var displayConfirmation = false;

        if (displayConfirmation){
            $("#contact-form").hide();
            $("#aticontactfooter").hide();
            $("#contact-form-confirmation").show();
            displayConfirmation = false;
            $("#myModal").modal('show');
        }          
    });

    /* ----- CHECK THE FORM DATA ----- */
    function check_form() {
        var error = false;
        var name = $("input[name=name]").val();
        var email = $("input[name=email]").val();
        var mess = $("textarea[name=message]").val();
        var company = $("input[name=company]").val();
        var phone = $("input[name=phone]").val();
        //var endUse = $("input[name=endUse]").val();

        var errorMessage = "";
        if (name.length < 1) {
            errorMessage += "Please enter your Name.\n";
            error = true;
        }
        if (email.length < 1 || email.indexOf("@") < 1) {
            errorMessage += "Please enter a valid Email address.\n";
            error = true;
        }
        if (mess.length < 1 || mess == "Type a message here.") {
            errorMessage += "Please enter a Message.\n";
            error = true;
        }

        if (company.length < 1) {
            errorMessage += "Please enter company name.\n";
            error = true;
        }

        if (phone.length < 1) {
            errorMessage += "Please enter a phone number.\n";
            error = true;
        }

        var greresponse = document.getElementById('ContactKey').value;

        if(greresponse.length == 0) {
            errorMessage += "reCAPTCHA not verified.\n";
            error = true;
        }

        if (error) { alert(errorMessage); return false;}
        else {
            $("input[title=submit]").click();
            $("#myModal").hide();
        }
    }
</script>

<script type="text/javascript"> 

    $(document).ready(function () {         
        var displayConfirmation = false;       
        if (displayConfirmation){
            $("#DownloadDataSheet-form").hide();
            $("#DataSheetDownloadfooter").hide();
            $("#downloaddatasheet-form-confirmation").show();
            displayConfirmation = false;   
            $("#DDModal").modal('show');
        }
    });
   
    function validateData() 
    {
        var error = false;
        var firstnameTextbox = $("input[name=firstnameTextbox]").val();
        var lastnameTextbox = $("input[name=lastnameTextbox]").val();
        var phoneTextbox = $("input[name=phoneTextbox]").val();
        var emailTextbox = $("input[name=emailTextbox]").val();
        var companyTextbox = $("input[name=companyTextbox]").val();
        var countryTextbox = $("input[name=countryTextbox]").val();
        var endUseTextbox = $("input[name=endUseTextbox]").val();
        //Non-Mandatory Fields
        var DataSheetname = $("input[name=datasheetName]").val();
        var SizeTextbox = $("input[name=sizeTextbox]").val();
        var ProductFormTextbox = $("input[name=productFormTextbox]").val();
        var FollowUp =$('#ctl00_ctl58_followupCheckbox').is(':checked') ? 'Yes' : 'No';      
       
        var errorMessage = "";
        if (firstnameTextbox.length < 1) {
            errorMessage += "Please enter your First Name.\n";
            error = true;
        }else
        { $("input[title=hdnFirstName]").val(firstnameTextbox);       
        }
       
        if (lastnameTextbox.length < 1 ) {
            errorMessage += "Please enter your Last Name.\n";
            error = true;
        }
        else
        { $("input[title=hdnLastName]").val(lastnameTextbox);       
        }

        if (phoneTextbox.length < 1) {
            errorMessage += "Please enter a valid Phone Number.\n";
            error = true;
        }else
        { $("input[title=hdnPhone]").val(phoneTextbox);       
        }

        if (emailTextbox.length < 1 || emailTextbox.indexOf("@") < 1) {
            errorMessage += "Please enter a valid Email address.\n";
            error = true;
        }else
        { $("input[title=hdnEmail]").val(emailTextbox);       
        }

        if (companyTextbox.length < 1) {
            errorMessage += "Please enter name of your Company.\n";
            error = true;
        }else
        { $("input[title=hdnCompany]").val(companyTextbox);       
        }

        if (countryTextbox.length < 1) {
            errorMessage += "Please enter Valid Country.\n";
            error = true;
        }else
        { $("input[title=hdnCountry]").val(countryTextbox);       
        }
     
        if (endUseTextbox.length < 1) {
            errorMessage += "Please enter company name.\n";
            error = true;
        } else
        { $("input[title=hdnEndUse]").val(endUseTextbox);       
        }              

        var captchaResponse = $("input[title=DDSKey]").val();
        if (captchaResponse.length == 0) {
            errorMessage += "reCAPTCHA not verified.\n";
            error = true;
        }

        if (SizeTextbox.length < 1) {
            SizeTextbox='N/A'; 
        }        
        if (ProductFormTextbox.length < 1) {
            ProductFormTextbox='N/A'; 
        }
                
        if (error) { alert(errorMessage); return false;}
        else 
        {            
            $("input[title=hdnSize]").val(SizeTextbox);           
            $("input[title=hdnProductForm]").val(ProductFormTextbox); 
            $("input[title=hdnFollowUp]").val(FollowUp);
            $("input[title=hdnDSheetName]").val(DataSheetname);
            $("input[title=submitDSRequest]").click();  
            $("#DDModal").hide();
        }
    } 
</script>
